            </ol>            
        </Block>        
    </Section>

    <Section Class="p-0" Size="HeadingSize.H4" Name="4. Troubleshooting" PageUrl="@pageUrl" Link="4-troubleshooting">
        <Block>
            <ul>
                <li>Ensure all CSS and JS references are correct in <code>index.html</code>.</li>
                <li>Restart the development server after making changes to static files.</li>
                <li>Check the browser console for errors if components do not render as expected.</li>
